  from, an ER_TRANSFORM_SOURCE_SRS_NOT_SUPPORTED
  (https://dev.mysql.com/doc/mysql-errors/8.0/en/server-error-reference
  .html#error_er_transform_source_srs_not_supported) error occurs.

