+---------------+
| JSON_TYPE(@j) |
+---------------+
| OBJECT        |
+---------------+
mysql> SELECT JSON_TYPE(JSON_EXTRACT(@j, '$.a'));
+------------------------------------+
| JSON_TYPE(JSON_EXTRACT(@j, '$.a')) |
+------------------------------------+
| ARRAY                              |
+------------------------------------+
